Initialises a newly created ConferencePaper object with attributes of the passed parameters.

Parameters:
IDNumber - ID number of a ConferencePaper, which is the primary key of a ConferencePaper, and is in format of "CP0000".
publicationTitle - Title of this ConferencePaper.
authorSet - A Set of author's full names, which may not be recorded in this system.
publishDate - The date this ConferencePaper is published, namely, is uploaded to this system. And is in Date type.
place - The place where this conference is hold.
uploaderUserName - The userName of the one who uploads this ConferencePaper.
